China to Promote Foreign Investment in Key Sectors, Daily Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-06-07T01:09:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-07/china-to-promote-foreign-investment-in-key-sectors-daily-says.html
China will revise guidelines on
foreign investment to encourage more overseas funds to enter
sectors considered of strategic importance to the nation, the
Economic Information Daily reported today, citing unnamed
officials at the National Development and Reform Commission.  China aims to promote investment to sectors such as auto
parts for new energy vehicles and recyclable water facilities,
the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  